Hello,

This email message is a notification to let you know that
a file has been uploaded to the Files area of the EVP-ITC 
group.

  File        : /Michael Edwards EVP RS 12-469/Nixon Nov 10 2008.wav 
  Uploaded by : f1cracker75 <f1cracker75@...> 
  Description : I was recording EVP for a client whose Dad died. I asked his dad who he saw when he crossed over, and he said usual stuff, uncles etc, but then he said this "One of us saw Nixon. The President".  

You can access this file at the URL:
